for part of the game. This is really, really simple. It worked well, especially since the

26
00:03:07,346 --> 00:03:12,868
game was very, very atmospheric and it worked really well just to have some music playing

27
00:03:12,868 --> 00:03:16,469
that was very atmospheric and didn't change very much.

28
00:03:16,469 --> 00:03:17,069
So before 2009 we had

29
00:03:23,372 --> 00:03:29,013
bunch of solutions handling the audio in the game. Most of it

30
