part of the whole system. So in the game, there are many different systems,

37
00:04:12,074 --> 00:04:20,238
lack of a better word. So we have empire space, which is basically

38
00:04:21,847 --> 00:04:27,311
pretty safe for players. Players start out there and they can go out and they can mine

39
00:04:27,311 --> 00:04:32,435
and do whatever they do when they start the game. It's pretty safe. The police is there.

40
00:04:32,435 --> 00:04:38,040
You're not attacked. The music can be really easy. And you can play old tracks like we

41
00:04:38,040 --> 00:04:39,921
have done. And the system, the new Eden, as we call,

42
00:04:48,392 --> 00:04:53,695
the space in Eve, it's called New Eden.

43
00:04:53,695 --> 00:04:55,496
It has more than 7,000 solar systems

44
00:04:55,496 --> 00:04:58,958
with I don't know how many moons and planets,

45
00:04:58,958 --> 00:05:01,480
just countless almost.

46
00:05:01,480 --> 00:05:08,184
And most often very safe to start in Empire Space,

47
00:05:08,184 --> 00:05:11,506
but if you go down to low sec and down to zero sec

48
00:05:11,506 --> 00:05:14,448
in wormhole space, it changes a lot.

49
00:05:14,448 --> 00:05:14,728
So.

50
00:05:21,634 --> 00:05:27,637
Usually it's not recommended for players to wander around and go to these places like

51
00:05:27,637 --> 00:05:33,701
Losac and Zero in the beginning at least. So they stay in Empire Space a lot.

52
00:05:33,701 --> 00:05:38,683
So the music in the game is based on these systems.

53
00:05:41,628 --> 00:05:47,632
So in Empire we have it easy going. In Low Sack we have it similar to Empire Space, but

54
00:05:47,632 --> 00:05:54,657
it has some more difficult intervals in the music maybe. And, you know, the timbre is

